node.text:
FRIENDS & HBO MAX... two of my favorite things🤩
I did better at the trivia than I expected but I still have some brushing up to do🤭
I’m obsessed with HBO MAX and all of the incredible content they have available. Definitely helping to keep me occupied during this quiet holiday season. If you’re thinking for a fun & safe way to pass the time you should sign up for @hbomax. Click the link in my bio to get 20% off when you prepay for a 6 month subscription. Restrictions apply. 
🤍
#ad
